---
title: Creamy Gochujang Beef Rigatoni with Spinach and Spring Onion
description: Sweet and spicy Korean style gochujang is the hero ingredient of this flavoursome Creamy Gochujang Beef Rigatoni, turning one of our favourite beef pasta dishes into something special for a weeknight dinner.
